{
  "id": "1PE.2",
  "bibleId": "de4e12af7f28f599-01",
  "number": "2",
  "bookId": "1PE",
  "reference": "1 Peter 2",
  "copyright": "PUBLIC DOMAIN except in the United Kingdom, where a Crown Copyright applies to printing the KJV. See http://www.cambridge.org/about-us/who-we-are/queens-printers-patent",
  "verseCount": 25,
  "content": [
    {
      "name": "para",
      "type": "tag",
      "attrs": {
        "style": "p"
      },
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "1",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1PE 2:1"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "1",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Wherefore laying aside all malice, and all guile, and hypocrisies, and envies, and all evil speakings, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.1",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.1"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "2",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1PE 2:2"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "2",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "As newborn babes, desire the sincere milk of the word, that ye may grow thereby: ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.2",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.2"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "3",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1PE 2:3"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "3",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "If so be ye have tasted that the Lord ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.3",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.3"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "is",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1PE.2.3",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1PE.2.3"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " gracious. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.3",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.3"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "4",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1PE 2:4"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "4",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "To whom coming, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.4",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.4"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "as unto",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1PE.2.4",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1PE.2.4"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " a living stone, disallowed indeed of men, but chosen of God, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.4",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.4"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "and",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1PE.2.4",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1PE.2.4"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " precious, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.4",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.4"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "5",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1PE 2:5"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "5",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Ye also, as lively stones, are built up a spiritual house, an holy priesthood, to offer up spiritual sacrifices, acceptable to God by Jesus Christ. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.5",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.5"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "6",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1PE 2:6"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "6",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Wherefore also it is contained in the scripture, Behold, I lay in Sion a chief corner stone, elect, precious: and he that believeth on him shall not be confounded. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.6",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.6"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "7",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1PE 2:7"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "7",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Unto you therefore which believe ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.7",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.7"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "he is",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1PE.2.7",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1PE.2.7"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " precious: but unto them which be disobedient, the stone which the builders disallowed, the same is made the head of the corner, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.7",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.7"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "8",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1PE 2:8"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "8",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And a stone of stumbling, and a rock of offence, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.8",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.8"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "even to them",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1PE.2.8",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1PE.2.8"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " which stumble at the word, being disobedient: whereunto also they were appointed. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.8",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.8"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "9",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1PE 2:9"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "9",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "But ye ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.9",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.9"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "are",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1PE.2.9",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1PE.2.9"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " a chosen generation, a royal priesthood, an holy nation, a peculiar people; that ye should shew forth the praises of him who hath called you out of darkness into his marvellous light: ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.9",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.9"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "10",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1PE 2:10"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "10",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Which in time past ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.10",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.10"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "were",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1PE.2.10",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1PE.2.10"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " not a people, but ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.10",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.10"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "are",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1PE.2.10",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1PE.2.10"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " now the people of God: which had not obtained mercy, but now have obtained mercy.",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.10",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.10"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "para",
      "type": "tag",
      "attrs": {
        "style": "p"
      },
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "11",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1PE 2:11"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "11",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Dearly beloved, I beseech ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.11",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.11"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "you",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1PE.2.11",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1PE.2.11"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " as strangers and pilgrims, abstain from fleshly lusts, which war against the soul; ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.11",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.11"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "12",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1PE 2:12"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "12",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Having your conversation honest among the Gentiles: that, whereas they speak against you as evildoers, they may by ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.12",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.12"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "your",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1PE.2.12",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1PE.2.12"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " good works, which they shall behold, glorify God in the day of visitation.",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.12",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.12"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "para",
      "type": "tag",
      "attrs": {
        "style": "p"
      },
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "13",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1PE 2:13"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "13",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Submit yourselves to every ordinance of man for the Lord’s sake: whether it be to the king, as supreme; ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.13",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.13"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "14",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1PE 2:14"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "14",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Or unto governors, as unto them that are sent by him for the punishment of evildoers, and for the praise of them that do well. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.14",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.14"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "15",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1PE 2:15"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "15",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "For so is the will of God, that with well doing ye may put to silence the ignorance of foolish men: ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.15",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.15"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "16",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1PE 2:16"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "16",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "As free, and not using ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.16",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.16"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "your",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1PE.2.16",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1PE.2.16"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " liberty for a cloke of maliciousness, but as the servants of God. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.16",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.16"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "17",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1PE 2:17"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "17",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Honour all ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.17",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.17"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "men",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1PE.2.17",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1PE.2.17"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": ". Love the brotherhood. Fear God. Honour the king. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.17",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.17"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "18",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1PE 2:18"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "18",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Servants, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.18",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.18"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "be",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1PE.2.18",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1PE.2.18"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " subject to ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.18",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.18"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "your",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1PE.2.18",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1PE.2.18"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " masters with all fear; not only to the good and gentle, but also to the froward. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.18",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.18"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "19",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1PE 2:19"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "19",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "For this ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.19",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.19"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "is",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1PE.2.19",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1PE.2.19"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " thankworthy, if a man for conscience toward God endure grief, suffering wrongfully. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.19",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.19"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "20",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1PE 2:20"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "20",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "For what glory ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.20",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.20"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "is it",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1PE.2.20",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1PE.2.20"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": ", if, when ye be buffeted for your faults, ye shall take it patiently? but if, when ye do well, and suffer ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.20",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.20"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "for it",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1PE.2.20",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1PE.2.20"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": ", ye take it patiently, this ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.20",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1PE.2.20"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "is",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1PE.2.20",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1PE.2.20"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " acceptable with God. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1PE.2.20",
